148
00:08:37.016 --> 00:08:38.476 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Thank you, Mama!

149
00:08:38.559 --> 00:08:39.435 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
A flower pattern?

150
00:08:40.436 --> 00:08:42.021 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
There’s nothing wrong with that.
It looks really cute.

151
00:08:42.104 --> 00:08:43.272 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Like a princess’ room.

152
00:08:43.356 --> 00:08:45.650 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
