166
00:09:26.315 --> 00:09:28.985 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
No way! That would be a problem!

167
00:09:30.444 --> 00:09:34.740 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Naoki’s really funny.
I never imagined him to be so outgoing.

168
00:09:34.824 --> 00:09:36.325 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I think we could get along.
That makes me happy.

169
00:09:36.409 --> 00:09:40.788 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Really? He made me super exhausted.
Fill up the tub for me, will you?

170
00:09:40.871 --> 00:09:42.665 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Oh, I did that already.

171
00:09:44.125 --> 00:09:48.129 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You don’t need to try
and be the perfect wife.

172
00:09:48.212 --> 00:09:50.423 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Let’s take a bath together and relax.

173
00:09:50.506 --> 00:09:52.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>I can’t relax doing that.</i>

174
00:09:55.136 --> 00:09:56.679 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
