176
00:10:00.516 --> 00:10:02.935 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Is your morning sickness that bad?

177
00:10:03.019 --> 00:10:06.314 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
