these past two, three days,

178
00:10:06.397 --> 00:10:08.608 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
perhaps because of the change
in atmosphere after moving.

179
00:10:08.691 --> 00:10:12.111 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Besides, I was getting a bit chubby,
so it’s perfect now.

180
00:10:12.194 --> 00:10:13.779 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I guess so.

181
00:10:15.031 --> 00:10:18.451 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
