184
00:10:25.082 --> 00:10:26.792 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
My mom and older sister are both chubby,

185
00:10:26.876 --> 00:10:30.713 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
and my younger sister goes through
great effort to maintain her great figure.

186
00:10:30.796 --> 00:10:33.549 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-How many siblings do you have?
-Two!

187
00:10:33.633 --> 00:10:35.843 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Both girls?
-Mm-hmm!

188
00:10:35.926 --> 00:10:39.555 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Wow, that’s kind of scary.
-There’s nothing scary about it.

189
00:10:39.639 --> 00:10:42.099 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
My older sister is
as kind as a bodhisattva.

190
00:10:42.183 --> 00:10:43.309 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Did you talk to your parents?

191
00:10:46.228 --> 00:10:48.814 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yeah. I called my mom.

192
00:10:49.940 --> 00:10:51.275 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
How much did you tell her?

193
00:10:53.986 --> 00:10:58.658 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
That I’m pregnant, so I might get married.

194
00:10:59.867 --> 00:11:03.412 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
What do you mean "might"?
Can’t you trust me?

195
00:11:03.496 --> 00:11:06.082 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-But…
-Oh well.

196
00:11:06.165 --> 00:11:08.584 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
And what did Mommy say?

197
00:11:08.668 --> 00:11:11.712 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Mommy? M-- Mommy said…

198
00:11:11.796 --> 00:11:15.841 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Oh, really? Congratulations. You did well.

199
00:11:15.925 --> 00:11:19.053 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Like that.
-What kind of mom is that?

200
00:11:19.136 --> 00:11:21.430 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
She’s that kind of mom.

201
00:11:21.514 --> 00:11:24.392 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
But I’ll bet your dad
is furious, isn’t he?

202
00:11:24.475 --> 00:11:25.559 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Not really.

203
00:11:25.643 --> 00:11:28.479 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Right after that call, he called me.

204
00:11:28.562 --> 00:11:29.522 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Rather than be angry,

205
00:11:29.605 --> 00:11:33.234 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
he just sighed and went on
about what a foolish daughter I am.

206
00:11:33.317 --> 00:11:35.486 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
He asked me what kind of man you are,

207
00:11:35.569 --> 00:11:39.115 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
so I told him that you work
in the music industry.

208
00:11:39.198 --> 00:11:42.118 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
He works at a karaoke joint?
Is it all-you-can-sing?

209
00:11:42.201 --> 00:11:44.036 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
That’s what he said.

210
00:11:44.870 --> 00:11:48.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
So I summed it up and told him
that you write music and stuff.

211
00:11:48.874 --> 00:11:50.418 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Summed it up?

212
00:11:50.501 --> 00:11:52.962 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Because if they found out
it’s Takumi of Trapnest,

213
00:11:53.045 --> 00:11:57.174 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
my younger sister will get all excited
and tell all her friends!

214
00:11:57.258 --> 00:12:00.094 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I haven’t even told
Jun-chan about this yet.

215
00:12:00.177 --> 00:12:01.303 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Jun-chan?

216
00:12:01.387 --> 00:12:04.181 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
She takes care of me like a mother,
even more than my real mother.

217
00:12:05.015 --> 00:12:08.102 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
She always lectures me,
but I feel her love for me.

218
00:12:08.185 --> 00:12:10.396 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Maybe Jun-chan’s the one
who gave birth to me.

219
00:12:10.479 --> 00:12:13.107 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
There’s no need to be secretive about this
to the people close to you.

220
00:12:13.190 --> 00:12:14.650 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I do have permission from the agency.

221
00:12:15.860 --> 00:12:20.573 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
We’ve decided to notify the media by fax
when the marriage becomes official.

222
00:12:20.656 --> 00:12:23.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Rather than trying to hide it,
it’s better to inform them

223
00:12:23.284 --> 00:12:26.162 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
and request them not to make a fuss about
it because I’m marrying an ordinary girl.

224
00:12:26.245 --> 00:12:29.331 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I’ve kept this coming Sunday open,

225
00:12:29.415 --> 00:12:31.459 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
so tell your parents that
I’ll be coming to meet them.

226
00:12:32.251 --> 00:12:36.589 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I’m hoping to discuss details
such as the wedding date then.

227
00:12:36.672 --> 00:12:39.967 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
We should make it soon,
before your belly begins to show.

228
00:12:44.847 --> 00:12:46.182 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
FROM: NAOKI
RE: REPORT

229
00:12:46.891 --> 00:12:49.310 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<i>I went to check out</i>
<i>Takumi and Hachiko’s new home!</i>

230
00:12:50.561 --> 00:12:54.023 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<i>Hachiko is a cute and nice girl,</i>
<i>and Takumi is very kind to her.</i>

231
00:12:54.106 --> 00:12:55.774 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<i>I’m sure things will go well</i>
<i>between the two.</i>

232
00:12:55.858 --> 00:12:57.359 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<i>There’s nothing to worry about.</i>

233
00:12:57.443 --> 00:13:00.321 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Good night. Heart.</i>

234
00:13:01.030 --> 00:13:03.115 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You’re disturbing my sleep!

235
00:13:24.637 --> 00:13:27.473 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
