290
00:17:33.218 --> 00:17:36.055 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I’m sorry. I got angry, so…

291
00:17:36.138 --> 00:17:38.307 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
