296
00:17:51.028 --> 00:17:52.404 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
A street musician?

297
00:17:52.488 --> 00:17:55.657 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
The lonely hero who wanders
