298
00:17:57.743 --> 00:17:59.787 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
That is so cool!

299
00:18:01.789 --> 00:18:04.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
