307
00:18:44.581 --> 00:18:50.379 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>but I will never forget the six months</i>
<i>we lived together.</i>

308
00:18:51.588 --> 00:18:56.927 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>It will be lonely not being able</i>
<i>to see you,</i>

309
00:18:57.010 --> 00:18:59.138 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>but I don’t know what to do.</i>

310
00:19:00.472 --> 00:19:04.143 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>So I hope that your major debut comes soon</i>

311
00:19:04.226 --> 00:19:06.728 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>and that you’ll be on TV a lot.</i>

312
00:19:06.812 --> 00:19:09.648 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Let me see you as you continue singing.</i>

313
00:19:10.649 --> 00:19:13.193 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>No matter who I’m in love with,</i>

314
00:19:13.277 --> 00:19:17.614 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>you will always be my only hero, Nana.</i>

315
00:19:19.074 --> 00:19:22.703 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>There’s nobody as cool as you.</i>

316
00:19:23.787 --> 00:19:27.082 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Until now… and from here on.</i>

317
00:19:27.166 --> 00:19:28.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
P.S. UNTIL YOU FIND A NEW ROOMMATE,

318
00:19:28.083 --> 00:19:28.917 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
