FOR MY SHARE OF THE APARTMENT.

319
00:19:29.001 --> 00:19:29.835 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I WILL LOCK THE DOOR ON MY WAY OUT.

320
00:19:29.918 --> 00:19:30.752 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I'LL SEE TO IT THAT REN GETS MY KEY.

321
00:19:32.838 --> 00:19:35.507 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
Why are you so sad?

322
00:19:38.093 --> 00:19:42.681 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
This is not a break-up letter
but a passionate love letter.

323
00:19:44.391 --> 00:19:48.770 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>You will always be my only hero, Nana.</i>

324
00:19:49.646 --> 00:19:51.732 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Go and visit Hachiko.

325
00:19:51.815 --> 00:19:54.151 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You do wanna see her tears of joy
when she sees you, right?

326
00:19:55.694 --> 00:19:59.531 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Why should I have to go see her?
That’s irrational!

327
00:20:03.535 --> 00:20:06.288 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
That’s what a hero does.

328
00:20:08.290 --> 00:20:10.167 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Good evening. Street Musician here.

329
00:20:10.250 --> 00:20:11.084 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Huh?

330
00:20:11.168 --> 00:20:12.628 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
MR. STREET MUSICIAN?

331
00:20:12.711 --> 00:20:16.506 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Are you alone? Can I come in?
-Sure.

332
00:20:21.470 --> 00:20:27.392 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Um, Shin… Mr. Street Musician.
I’m sorry about the other day.

333
00:20:27.976 --> 00:20:29.770 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I, Shinichi Okazaki, will now sing.

334
00:20:46.662 --> 00:20:52.167 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Hey, Hachi… No matter how much</i>
<i>or how often people hurt each other…</i>

335
00:20:52.251 --> 00:20:56.421 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>loving someone is never a waste.</i>

336
00:20:58.882 --> 00:21:05.639 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Even now, I still cherish that</i>
<i>love letter you gave me then.</i>

